Skyline



...as seen from the Space Needle. We should have gone up again: Rainier was hiding behind clouds (in the center of the photo) but it was much clearer the following two days and we had a great view of the mountain from the airport as we left.
Taken Sunday, July 20, 2003, 02:27:55pm.  Original image size: 3072x1728, 6.2Mb
Technical details: Canon EOS D60, 1/800s @ F8.0, ISO 100, 15mm/F2.8 (24mm equiv)
